    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear with some staining on the carpets and a small tear in the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price of a mint-condition model.",
      "price": 22500.0,
