    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The engine has a noticeable knock and struggles to maintain idle, while the transmission exhibits slipping between gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal donor car or a major project for someone with mechanical expertise.",
