    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into reliability with this well-maintained vehicle! It's in good condition and has clearly been cared for, offering a smooth ride and a clean appearance that\u2019s ready for the road. This is a fantastic opportunity to own a dependable car that looks great and performs even better. Come see why this solid choice is perfect for your daily commute!",
      "price": 35000.0,
